query:
SELECT gi.id, gi.prompt, gi.generatedImageUrl, gi.aspectRatio, gi.resolution, gi.taskId, gi.createdAt 
FROM generatedImages gi 
JOIN users u ON gi.userId = u.id 
WHERE u.email = 'beygovau@gmail.com' 
ORDER BY gi.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 10;
